comments: Sengun (HOU is moving alongside Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Sengun (HOU) does not maintain legal guarding position and makes contact with Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Porter Jr. (HOU) is already in Morant's (MEM) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Sengun (HOU) is firming up over his left leg and marginal contact occurs with Bane (MEM) during the pick.
Bane (MEM) legally contests Green's (HOU) jump shot attempt.
Sengun (HOU) extends his arms into Jackson Jr. (MEM) and dislodges him from his legally obtained rebounding position.
Green (HOU) is already in Bane's (MEM) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.

Replay review of the foul called on Morant (MEM) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Sengun (HOU) initiates contact with Morant, who has established a legal guarding position in his path.  The call is overturned to an offensive foul on Sengun.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) and Green (HOU) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Porter Jr. (HOU) is moving alongside Bane's (MEM) path and marginal contact occurs as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Eason (HOU) avoids making contact with Bane's (MEM) arm has he defends the driving shot attempt.
Martin Jr. (HOU) brings his hands towards Bane (MEM) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away from the contact.
Roddy (MEM) is drawn into the air on a pump fake and initiates contact with Martin Jr. (HOU) as he defends the shot near the rim.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) cleanly blocks Martin Jr.'s (HOU) shot attempt while the ball is on its upward flight to the basket and before the shot has reached its apex.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) is already in Green's (HOU) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Smith Jr. (HOU) is moving alongside Bane's (MEM) path and marginal contact occurs as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Eason (HOU) is retreating his arm into a vertical position and marginal contact occurs with Bane's (MEM) left arm as he  removes his left hand from the ball.
Morant (MEM) cleanly deflects the ball away from Green (HOU).  Any ensuing contact with Green's side after the deflection is considered incidental.
Bane (MEM) brings his hands towards Porter Jr. (HOU) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away to receive the inbound pass.
Eason (HOU) commits a take foul on Kennard (MEM).
Morant (MEM) swipes his arm down and makes contact with Green's (HOU) arm that causes Green to lose control of the ball.
Eason (HOU) commits a take foul on Bane (MEM). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of the fourth quarter and overtime.
Bane (MEM) maintains verticality as he defends Porter Jr.'s (HOU) driving shot attempt.
Eason (HOU) and Bane (MEM) each make clean contact with the ball as they pursue the rebound.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) legally contests Martin Jr.'s (HOU) shot at the rim.
Eason (HOU) commits a take foul on Bane (MEM).
